# Frontend for ocs 
	This is a frontend written in polymer (https://www.polymer-project.org/1.0/) to interact
	with REST API provided in ocs application. 

## Prerequisites

	You need to have following installed on your computer.
	1. nodejs (https://nodejs.org/en/download/)
	2. git (https://git-scm.com/)

## Installation 

	Install bower on your computer.
	$ npm install -g bower

## Building

	1. Once bower is installed, go to directory where bower.json is located.
	$ cd $OCS_ROOT_DIRECTORY/frontend

	2. Install all the required polymer dependencies with following command. This will save
	all the dependencies in $OCS_ROOT_DIRECTORY/frontend/bower_components directory.
	$ bower install


